title: The Time Tunnel - The Walls Of Jericho Ep. 20
description: Doug and Tony are transported to the camp of Joshua, the leader of the Israelites. Tony discloses secrets that only Joshua knows and he believes the two time travelers have been sent by God. He assigns them to spy on the city of Jericho. The two scientists help the sister of Rahab but Doug is captured by the captain and arrested and thrown in Jericho's dungeons.
